###

### 查看当前模式
GET http://127.0.0.1:8082/mode

###

### 切换为多 AI 协同模式
POST http://127.0.0.1:8082/mode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "multi"
}

###

### 切换为单 AI 模式（DeepSeek 直出）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8082/mode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "single"
}

###

### 测试 OpenClaw Webhook 接收接口
POST http://127.0.0.1:8082/webhook/openclaw
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "req",
  "id": "fd58351c-b11e-4aa2-afb9-fd4f7f5bb6ea",
  "method": "chat.send",
  "params": {
    "sessionKey": "agent:main:main",
    "message": "Hello Relic！",
    "deliver": false,
    "idempotencyKey": "cd453e61-9c8a-42c8-83b5-c2d30ab5f26b"
  }
}